workflow.name: Generate stock market investment reports from FinancialDatasets.ai with AI
workflow.description:
# üöÄ **Perfect if you are...**

- üí∞ **Beginner Investor** ‚Äì Learn the market faster with AI-powered insights guiding your decisions.
- üìà **Retail Trader** ‚Äì Optimize your trading strategy with in-depth analysis typically reserved for professionals.
- üè¶ **Hedge Fund & Institutional Trader** ‚Äì Automate high-level market analysis using advanced AI models.
- ü§ñ **Automation Enthusiast** ‚Äì Get hands-on with **n8n** and build an automated stock research tool.

---

# ‚ùî **What It Does:**

‚úÖ **AI-Driven Investment Reports** ‚Äì Our system analyzes **30,000+ tickers** with historical data spanning **30+ years**. It provides **fundamental, technical, and sentiment analysis** in a structured, easy-to-read report.

‚úÖ **Your Personal Hedge Fund on Your PC** ‚Äì AI-powered advisors analyze **earnings reports, insider trades, stock prices, financial metrics, and news**, delivering precise, data-driven recommendations tailored to you.

‚úÖ **Real Advisors, Real Insights** ‚Äì Our system replicates the thought processes of **investing legends** like Warren Buffett, Charlie Munger, Cathie Wood, and Ben Graham, offering multiple expert-style perspectives on every stock decision.

‚úÖ **Ultra Low Cost** ‚Äì Running this workflow costs **less than $0.30 per report** (*AI model costs not included*). That‚Äôs cheaper than a cup of coffee, yet it provides insights worth thousands of dollars.

---
# üõ†Ô∏è **Initial Setup**

- Visit [FinancialDatasets.ai](FinancialDatasets.ai) and retrieve your API key.
- Locate the **HTTPS Nodes** (üåê) and insert your API key under the header **X-API-KEY** in each one.
- In the **Gmail node**, ensure you set up the email where you want to receive your reports.
- Test your workflow by typing the name of a company or the stock ticker in the chat. Your report should arrive within 10 minutes.

---

# üß™ **Customize It!**

- To modify the **workflow triggers**, change the trigger type and **update the message that the Ticker Extractor receives** in this part of the prompt:  
  `"Based on this message, =={{ $json.chatInput }}== "`  
  *This prevents any disruptions in the workflow.*

- To **change the report destination**, update the node type. You can send reports to **Telegram, Slack, or other platforms** instead of Gmail.

- Each **advisor's personality** is configured through its system message‚Äîfeel free to tweak it to suit your needs.

- You can **create new agents** by duplicating an existing one and assigning it a different personality.  
  **Remember to reference the new agent in the linked nodes** to ensure seamless integration.


----

‚ö†Ô∏è **Important Note:**  
This workflow requires an **API key from [FinancialDatasets.ai](FinancialDatasets.ai)** to access stock market data.

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
